<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Password Reset Successful</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{background:#f0f2f5;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif}.wrapper{max-width:600px;margin:40px auto;background:#fff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}.header{background:#0d1f4f;padding:28px 40px;text-align:center}.header h1{color:#fff;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px}.body{padding:40px}.greeting{font-size:1rem;color:#0d1f4f;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px}.text{font-size:.92rem;color:#555;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px}.success-box{text-align:center;margin:28px 0}.success-icon{width:72px;height:72px;background:#d1e7dd;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 16px;font-size:2rem}.btn{display:inline-block;background:#e8610a;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem}.divider{height:1px;background:#eee;margin:28px 0}.alert-box{background:#f8d7da;border-left:4px solid #dc3545;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:20px}.alert-box p{font-size:.85rem;color:#842029;line-height:1.6}.footer{background:#f4f6fb;padding:24px 40px;text-align:center}.footer p{font-size:.8rem;color:#aaa;line-height:1.6}.footer a{color:#e8610a;text-decoration:none}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header"><h1>LOVELISTICS</h1></div>
    <div class="body">
        <p class="greeting">Hi <%= fullName %>,</p>

        <div class="success-box">
            <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
            <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#0d1f4f;margin-bottom:8px;">Password Reset Successful</p>
            <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:#888;">Your password has been updated successfully.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
            <a href="<%= appUrl %>" class="btn">Login to Your Account →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="alert-box">
            <p>🚨 If you did not reset your password, please contact us immediately at <strong>support@lovelistics.com</strong> as your account may be compromised.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text" style="font-size:.82rem;">
            For security, we recommend using a strong, unique password that you don't use on other websites.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@lovelistics.com">support@lovelistics.com</a><br/>© 2026 LOVELISTICS. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>